<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('../partials/head'); %>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <%- include('../partials/sellerHeader'); %>
</header>

<main>
    <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
          <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
          <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
          <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
        </ol>
        <div id="divCarousel" class="carousel-inner">
          <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img class="d-block w-100 h-80" src="https://files.porsche.com/filestore/image/multimedia/none/po-416-r4-detail-audioandcommunication-bose-xle/zoom/36a1e351-3ff6-11e3-bd76-001a64c55f5c;s3/porsche-zoom.jpg" alt="First slide">
            <div class="carousel-caption d-block">
                <h5>Ofertas</h5>
                <p>Aprovecha hasta un 20% de descuento</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img class="d-block w-100 justify-center" src="https://photos.enjoei.com.br/public/1200x1200/czM6Ly9waG90b3MuZW5qb2VpLmNvbS5ici9wcm9kdWN0cy85ODE5NTMwLzg3MmJlMDY3ZGM2ZDRhY2M0NjkxMjgzOTMwN2U5NWY5LmpwZw" alt="Second slide">
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img class="d-block w-100" src="https://blog.br.playstation.com/tachyon/sites/4/2020/04/FEAT_DS-1.jpg" alt="Third slide">
          </div>
        </div>
        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
          <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>
        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
          <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-light ">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
            <img class="mt-5"src="/images/logoAzul.png" width="55" height="50" alt="">
            <h1 class="mt-5 text-primary"><%= title %></h1>
        </div>
        <div class="container text-center text-secondary">
            <p>Digitienda es una plataforma en la que puedes 
                vender y comprar productos de la manera más sencilla. 
                ¡Únete<br> a esta gran comunidad y realiza tu primera 
                compra o vende tu primer producto1  
            </p>
          
        </div>
        <div id="addProduct" class="align-center">
            <button class="btn btn-primary ml-5 mb-5" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#exampleModal" data-whatever="@mdo"><i class="bi bi-plus"></i>Publicar producto</button>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white">
            <br>
            <br>
            <h4 class="ml-5 mb-5">Explora la variedad de productos que otros vendedores tienen para ofrecer.</h3>
            <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center bg-white">
                <% products.forEach(function(product) { %>
                    <div class="card mr-5 mb-5" style="width: 18rem;">
                        <img class="card-img-top" src="/images/product.jpeg" alt="Card image cap">
                        <div class="card-body">
                          <h5 class="card-title"><strong><%= product.name %></strong></h5>
                          <p class="card-text"><%= product.description %></p>
                          <p class="card-text">Precio: $<%= product.price %></p>
                          <a href="/Producto" class="btn btn-primary">Ver producto</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% }); %>
            </div>
        </div>
        
    </div>
    <!--Modal-->
    <div class="modal fade" id="exampleModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
            <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h5 class="modal-title" id="exampleModalLabel">Publica un producto</h5>
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                </button>
            </div>

            <form class="" onsubmit='return registerProduct(this, event);' method='post'>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="recipient-name" class="col-form-label">Nombre del producto*</label>
                        <input id="name" type="text" class="form-control" id="recipient-name">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="message-text" class="col-form-label">Descripción*</label>
                        <textarea id="description" class="form-control" id="message-text"></textarea>
                        <small class="form-text text-muted">10-150 palabras</small>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="message-text" class="col-form-label">Característica 1</label>
                        <textarea id="carac1" class="form-control" id="message-text"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="message-text" class="col-form-label">Característica 2</label>
                        <textarea id="carac2" class="form-control" id="message-text"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="message-text" class="col-form-label">Característica 3</label>
                        <textarea id="carac3" class="form-control" id="message-text"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="recipient-name" class="col-form-label">Precio (MXN)*</label>
                        <input id="price" type="number" class="form-control" id="recipient-name">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="recipient-name" class="col-form-label">Stock inicial (Número de unidades disponibles)*</label>
                        <input id="stock" type="number" class="form-control" id="recipient-name">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="exampleFormControlSelect1">Categoría*</label>
                        <select id="category" class="form-control" id="exampleFormControlSelect1">
                            <option value="1">Electrónicos</option>
                            <option value="2">Calzado</option>
                            <option value="3">Artículos para el hogar</option>
                            <option value="4">Herramientas</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="col form-group">
                            <label for="exampleFormControlFile1">Foto 1*</label>
                            <div class="custom-file">
                                <input id="img1" type="file" class="custom-file-input" id="validatedCustomFile">
                                <label class="custom-file-label" for="validatedCustomFile">Elija una foto...</label>
                                <div class="invalid-feedback">Debe seleccionar una foto</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col form-group">
                            <label for="exampleFormControlFile1">Foto 2*</label>
                            <div class="custom-file">
                                <input id="img2" type="file" class="custom-file-input" id="validatedCustomFile">
                                <label class="custom-file-label" for="validatedCustomFile">Elija una foto...</label>
                                <div class="invalid-feedback">Debe seleccionar una foto</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="col form-group">
                            <label for="exampleFormControlFile1">Foto 3*</label>
                            <div class="custom-file">
                                <input id="img3" type="file" class="custom-file-input" id="validatedCustomFile">
                                <label class="custom-file-label" for="validatedCustomFile">Elija una foto...</label>
                                <div class="invalid-feedback">Debe seleccionar una foto</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col form-group">
                            <label for="exampleFormControlFile1">Foto 4*</label>
                            <div class="custom-file">
                                <input id="img4" type="file" class="custom-file-input" id="validatedCustomFile">
                                <label class="custom-file-label" for="validatedCustomFile">Elija una foto...</label>
                                <div class="invalid-feedback">Debe seleccionar una foto</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <div class="addProduct">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Cancelar</button>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Publicar producto</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>
<footer>
    <%- include('../partials/footerSeller'); %>
</footer>
</body>
</html>